Version History

Version 1.0 

This is the first release of the System.PAM module. Functionality for the following 
PAM operations are provided in this release:

start(), end(), authenticate(), chauthtok(), open_session(), close_session(), 
strerror(), setcreds(), get_item(), and set_item()

Version 1.2

Added testsuite.in so that the module will install automatically with monger.

Added configure tests for pam header files on linux and darwin (macos x).

Version 1.3

Added acconfig.h file for users with different versions of autoheader 
don't have problems.
